\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s'</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.regs\">regs</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s₂</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.regs\">regs</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Reverse halting: if p.toStandardForm reaches a halted state, p reaches a halted state\nwith the same registers. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Steps.from_toStandardForm_halts","kind":"theorem","line":190,"name":"Cslib.URM.Steps.from_toStandardForm_halts","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.lean#L190-L208"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Step.from_toStandardForm\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">from_toStandardForm</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">s'</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State\">State</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hstep</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step\">Step</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <spa