a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s₂</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.isHalted\">isHalted</a></span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s'</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.regs\">regs</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s₂</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.regs\">regs</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Forward halting: if p reaches a halted state, p.toStandardForm reaches a halted state\nwith the same registers. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Steps.toStandardForm_halts","kind":"theorem","line":127,"name":"Cslib.URM.Steps.toStandardForm_halts","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.lean#L127-L143"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Step.toStandardForm\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Step</span>.<span class=\"name\">toStandardForm</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">s'</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State\">State</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hstep</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step\">Step</a> <span class=\"fn\">p</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">s'</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step\">Step</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">s'</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Or\">∨</a>   <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s'</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.isHalted\">isHalted</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">p</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\">∃ (<span class=\"fn\">s₂</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State\">State</a>), <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Execution.html#Cslib.URM.Step\">Step</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span> <span class=\"fn\">s₂</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s₂</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.isHalted\">isHalted</a></span> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#And\">∧</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s'</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.regs\">regs</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">s₂</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.State.regs\">regs</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Forward step correspondence: if p steps from s to s', then either:\n(1) p.toStandardForm steps from s to s' (same step), or\n(2) s' is halted in p, and p.toStandardForm steps to a state that is also halted\n    with the same registers (this only happens for jumps with unbounded targets). ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Step.toStandardForm","kind":"theorem","line":93,"name":"Cslib.URM.Step.toStandardForm","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.lean#L93-L125"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.straight_line_IsStandardForm\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">straight_line_IsStandardForm</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hsl</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StraightLine.html#Cslib.URM.Program.IsStraightLine\">IsStraightLine</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.IsStandardForm\">IsStandardForm</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Straight-line programs are in standard form. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.straight_line_IsStandardForm","kind":"theorem","line":79,"name":"Cslib.URM.straight_line_IsStandardForm","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.lean#L79-L83"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm_idempotent\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\">Program</span>.<span class=\"name\">toStandardForm_idempotent</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/Defs.html#Cslib.URM.Program\">Program</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">p</span>.<a href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm\">toStandardForm</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"toStandardForm is idempotent: applying it twice equals applying it once. ","docLink":"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm_idempotent","kind":"theorem","line":66,"name":"Cslib.URM.Program.toStandardForm_idempotent","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/cslib/blob/b00648a4fe741981bb586a3cc845258ab1583f61/Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.lean#L66-L73"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Cslib/Computability/URM/StandardForm.html#Cslib.URM.Program.getElem?_toStandardForm\"><span class=\"name\">Cslib</span>.<span class=\"name\">URM</span>.<span class=\"name\